title: Grateful Dead Live at The Centrum on 1988-04-07
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi DR-8 (no Dolby) > Audiophile 2496 analog-in > Soundforge > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC. Transferred by Andrew F. Feb 2008. - surround mixing by Kevin Tobin
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Feel Like A Stranger, Franklin's Tower, Minglewood Blues, Row Jimmy, Memphis Blues, Big Railroad Blues, Around & Around

Set 2

Sugar Magnolia-> Scarlet Begonias-> Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> All Along The Watchtower-> Black Peter-> Sunshine Daydream, E: Box Of Rain

FM Broadcast WCUW
